    <p>where:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><codeph>debug=true</codeph> is a parameter for map views</li>
      <li><codeph>partition</codeph>  is the vBucket ID where the document that produced this row
        (emitted by the map function) lives</li>
      <li><codeph>node</codeph> tells from which node in the cluster the row came (value “local” for
        the node that received the query, or an URL otherwise).</li>
    </ul>
   
    <p>Doing the same query against the replica index ( <codeph>_type=replica</codeph> ) gives the
      following result:</p>
